name: Art Roadmap 1.0
description: I have been wondering for a while if I can create an xcopyesque piece with code. I've started that quest now. Etherinsight art roadmap 1.0. Here's my attempt at drawing eyeballs. The one black eyeball stands out from all others. I didn't plan to make one different but this unintended action has created something interesting. It's like queen bee surrounded by other bees. Whose is that single eyeball?  Made with drawbot and python code.
